data.description: Come see this fantastic 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bath Home! You will fall in love with the formal dining w/ beautiful wood laminate flooring which flows into the spacious living room.  Picture yourself escaping into the huge master located on main floor and soak in the lovely Spa tub or head upstairs and hang out in the oversized loft/game room!  If you like to entertain then you will adore the extended stained concrete covered Patio where memories for years to come can be made.  If you are a Chef in the kitchen then you will adore this kitchen which has miles of counter space and plenty of storage & adjoins a cute breakfast area. Conveniently located near Lackland AFB, Sea World, Northwest Vista college and Alamo Ranch everything you need is minutes away! Schedule a showing today!
